<!DOCTYPE airframe SYSTEM "../airframe.dtd">
<!-- Parkzone Extra 300 (http://www.parkzone.com/Products/Default.aspx?ProdID=PKZ5180)
     LIsa M v2.0  (http://paparazzi.enac.fr/wiki/index.php/)
     With modified power routing by Jumper J1
     * Aspirine v2.1 inclusive MS5611
     * XBee XSC 900Mhz
     * uBlox LEA5H and Sarantel helix GPS antenna

     Near Future
     * Current and voltage sensor
     * Airspeed sensor via I2C

     NOTES:
      no special things (for now)

READ this first
http://paparazzi.enac.fr/w/index.php?title=Theory_of_Operation
